tafsir[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,122,"JaЕӢtii an Annabiijo, ko heЙ“unoo feddeeji Й—iЙ—i jeyaaЙ—i e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en; immorde e Banii Salamah e Banii Haaritha, fewndo Й“e lo'unoo, Й“e huli yiltagol ka hare tuma nde naafiqi en ruttinoo. Ko Allah woni Walloowo Й“en Й—on sabu tabitugol ngol e hare nden firta ko Й“e himmirnoo yiltagol. Ko Alla Tan woni gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haani tuuginorde e fiyakuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in."
  3,123,"GomЙ—ii Alla Wallii on e dow sirkooЙ“e Й“en ka hare Badri, tawi ko on waawaaЙ“e; sabu famЙ—ugol limoore e joga. Hulee Alla, belajo'o, on yettay Neemaaji Makko Й—in e dow mo'on."
  3,124,"JaЕӢto an Annabiijo, tuma wi'annoЙ—aa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ka hare Badri, hiЙ—a felliЕӢtinana Й“e ko Й“e nani e fii Й“eyditireede ko haЙ“a sirkooЙ“e Й“en: "Enee, yonaЕӢtaa on nde Alla Wallirta on Malaa'ikaaЙ“e guluuje tato jippiЕӢtiiЙ“e immorde ka Makko KaЕӢko SeniiЙ—o On, ko wallitoo on e ndee hare?!"."
  3,125,"Pellet [ko non woniri], Й—um yonay on. No woodani on wewlere Ballal Alla goo : si on muГұГұike e hare nden, on hulii Alla, on Й“eydiraama woЙ—Й“e goo ardooЙ“e yaccaare ko wallitoo on e ayЙ“e Й“en; Й—um fow si waЙ—ii, haray Joomi mon Walliray on guluuje jowi Malaa'ika maandiraaЙ“e e mun kaГұum e pucci mun; maandeeji feeГұuЙ—i."
  3,126,"Alla WaЙ—iraali ngal Ballal e Й“eydireede Malaa'ika si wanaa welo-welo wonannde on, e no Й“erЙ—e mon Й—eeЖҙira e Й—um. Si wanaa Й—um, ballal ngal tigiri newortaako Й—in sabuuji feeГұuЙ—i Й—on tun, si ko woni, Ballal ngal tigiri ko ka Alla Iwrata, on FooluЙ—o mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e KuuЙ—e mun."
  3,127,"Ngal Ballal ngal Й“e walliraa ka hare Badri, Alla Faandorike ngal halkugol fedde e Й“en yedduЙ“e hare nden, O Hoyna fedde goo, O Tikkinira Й“e fooleede nden; Й“e ruttoroo koyeera e jaasera."
  3,128,"Tuma nde NulaaЙ—o on huЙ—irnoo mawbe sirkooЙ“e Й“en halakuyee Й“aawo fooleede Й“e "Uhud", Alla Daalani mo: "Huunde alanaa ma e fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on, Й—um ko juuЙ—e Alla woni, muГұГұo haa Гұalnde Alla Г‘aawata hakkunde mo'on, maa O Hawrinndina Й“e e tuubugol silma, maa Й“e duumoo e keeferaaku O Leptira Й“e Й—um; pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e tooГұooЙ“e hannduЙ“e e lepte"."
  3,129,"Ko Alla Woodani Tagugol Toppitoo kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo Haforana junuubi on mo O Muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e yurmeende Makko, O leptira on mo O Muuyi NunЙ—al Makko. Alla ko Haforanoowo kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, yurmotooЙ—o Й“e."
  3,130,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, woЙ—Й—itee e ribaa -cowalle sowaaЙ—i e hoore ko*e jawle mon nyamlirton kunwano majjunooЙ“e gerdaynoo. Hulee Alla, Й—oftoЙ—on Yamirooje Makko, woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko; belajo'o, on daГұan ko Й—aЙ“Й“oton kon e moЖҙЖҙere aduna e laakara."
  3,131,"WaЙ—ee hakkunde mon e ngen yiite maranaange heeferЙ“e Й“en, daЙ—ndal. ЖҠum non, ko gollugol ko moЖҙЖҙi, tertoo ko harmi."
  3,132,"ЖҠoftoree Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e jokkugol YamiraaЙ—i Й—in, woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Й—in. Beajo'o, on daГұan Yumeede aduna e laakara."